definitions.definition: To live as a bachelor ; (chiefly of a man) to live without women, and do one's own cooking, housekeeping etc.
definitions.label_groups: Canada , US , Australia , New Zealand , now rare

main_definition: ( Canada , US , Australia , New Zealand , now rare ) To live as a bachelor ; (chiefly of a man) to live without women, and do one's own cooking, housekeeping etc.
